We can all smell it
On the wind
A sundering summery stench
Pitches a concept 
Let it be open
Let us be visible
Paperwork gives way to a red typhoon
Tinder for the forst fire
When is it time to retire? 
And when you give in,
And your heart ignites?
Then is the time to retire?
Then is it time to take flight?
